<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Rex</ENAMEX> , an overseas <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Chinese</ENAMEX> from <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">South Africa</ENAMEX> , who began his career as a trainer at <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">California Fitness Centers</ENAMEX> , took notice of this wave beginning to build <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">three years ago</ENAMEX> , and returned to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> to devote himself to the local market .
