" If health centers can offer not only working out but also recreational functions , then members will keep coming back , " says <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Tang</ENAMEX> .
" Modern urban life is stressful and fast - paced , and sometimes a member may be more in need of the relaxation provided by a sauna or aroma - therapy .
